{"tid":1084260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★游蕙禎晒比堅尼照 網民笑指轉搞「睇肉」","createTime":"2019-03-30T09:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T11:27:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea1824353a25caad1891929d0e6e31f2a4e0bb5","tid":1084260,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:18:36.000Z","msg":"前立法會議員游蕙禎近期積極發展網紅事業，不時為產品賣吓廣告，今日更在IG貼出比堅尼照，令粉絲眼前一亮，短短兩小時就吸逾3000個Like。<br />\n游蕙禎在IG嘅貼文表示「非常濕焗嘅天氣。好想落泳池浸全日。數數下都成十幾年冇去過公眾泳池。自從第一單泳池發現糞便案開始，我就自此唔再去，因為覺得太污糟，同埋太多人，踢下腳分分鐘都會踢親隔離個婆婆咁。唔知而家大家仲有冇去泳池嘅習慣？」<br />\n雖然佢問大家有無去泳池游水，但網民似乎比較注意佢穿上白色比堅尼，橫臥在巨型浮床嘅造型照。有網民對照片表示讚賞，仲話要約佢一齊遊；亦有網民笑指游蕙禎不搞政治，轉搞「睇肉」，游蕙禎則回應「我只不過係影Ｄ每個人都有嘅野然後放上網，你自己都有，可以睇自己。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1468830/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1468830%2F&d=Ru8OiKpQtXbNv5YRwinC6oVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=cdd55d8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1468830%2F&h=28a85966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1468830/</a>"},{"pid":"67082dd02075c9762bfa0c0fe313865339630604","tid":1084260,"uid":25019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ac3c957e3fcfcfe3b37800b7e0186e251babcb","tid":1084260,"uid":13804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"想同游b玩遊戲"},{"pid":"1145760e9452e2c304640645a511d9b2e3b66e0f","tid":1084260,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ac3c957e3fcfcfe3b37800b7e0186e251babcb","tid":1084260,"uid":13804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"想同游b玩遊戲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.g